txt.en: 'Why so tired now?'
'That is my barrel!'
'Time to nap!'
'Nightshade... sleep.'
'Maybe here is good place to rest.'
The gate to the Left Wing has closed, sealing the wing
'What are you doing? Get up! I told you to leave the barrels alone!'
This chest can be used if most of the prisoners are rescued.
A prisoner has escaped from the Right Wing. The gate begins to close as alarms sound
The Toughs in the Right Wing are preparing to close the gates to the wing
The gate to the Right Wing has closed, sealing the wing
The Toughs in the Right Wing have detected intruders. They are on alert
'Did you really think you could escape the dungeons of Dol Guldur alive?!'
'Come back! I fear being alone....'
'All you have managed to do is to collect our enemies into one room!'
'Please do not leave me! I am afraid....'
'Now you too shall share our prisoners' fate! You shall never leave this place alive!'
'I am afraid! Please do not leave my side!'
'We are free!'
The Toughs in the Central Wing are preparing to close the gates to the wing
'You did it!'
'You are truly a hero!'
The Toughs in the Central Wing have detected intruders. They are on alert
'Well done, indeed!'
This chest can be used if less than most the prisoners are rescued.
'Thank you! I will live to fight another day!'
'I will see the sky once again!'
'A day that will go down in history!'
'Your name will be sung for ages!'
'I never dreamed I would live through this.'
The Toughs have closed the gate to the Right Wing, sealing the wing
This chest can be used if more than a few of the prisoners are rescued.
The gate to the Central Wing has closed, sealing the wing
A prisoner has escaped from the Central Wing. The gate begins to close as alarms sound
'Intruders! Imprison them! Do not let any escape!'
The Toughs in the Left Wing are preparing to close the gates to the wing
The Toughs have closed the gate to the Central Wing, sealing the wing
'Why did the Warden tell us stay away from barrels?'
This chest can be used if only a few of the prisoners are rescued.
The Toughs in the Left Wing have detected intruders. They are on alert
'I was planning on sparing some of your lives. No longer!'
'Oh thank you! I will wait in the court for you to rescue the others....'
'Is this how you want to play then? Terror will be my ally!'
'Thank the Valar you have returned! Please do not leave me again!'
'You must not leave me again! I was so afraid!'
'You have come back! Let us continue then....'
'By Durin's beard!'
'I feared I would die in this place.'
'Thank the Valar! You have come to rescue me?'
'Stay close!'
'I thought for certain that I would die in this place....'
'Get your hands off of my Nightshade!'
'Let us go! And please, stay close to me... I do not want to be alone again.'
'Who knows? I want to see what is all the fuss!'
'Mmmmpphh...'
'Hmmpphh... mmmph...'
The Toughs have closed the gate to the Left Wing, sealing the wing
'Hurmmpph...'
This chest can be used once the Warden is killed.
'Snorffmmpphh...'
A prisoner has escaped from the Left Wing. The gate begins to close as alarms sound
